1
00:02:09,000 --> 00:02:15,999
"To My Shore."

2
00:02:16,000 --> 00:02:17,600
The guy who molested me.

3
00:02:20,520 --> 00:02:21,800
I found him.

4
00:02:22,160 --> 00:02:23,478
He's here, in this club.

5
00:02:23,479 --> 00:02:24,600
How did you find him?

6
00:02:24,679 --> 00:02:26,239
Let's go hear what he has to say first.

7
00:02:47,119 --> 00:02:48,160
I'll go scout ahead.

8
00:02:58,720 --> 00:02:59,839
Who the hell are you?

9
00:02:59,960 --> 00:03:01,080
Young Master Bai.

10
00:03:01,759 --> 00:03:02,559
I need a word with you.

11
00:03:02,560 --> 00:03:03,679
Turn the lights back on.

12
00:03:03,880 --> 00:03:05,240
Clear the room.

13
00:03:07,520 --> 00:03:08,520
Who the hell is this?

14
00:03:08,559 --> 00:03:09,399
Weird.

15
00:03:09,479 --> 00:03:10,479
Who the hell are you?

16
00:03:10,520 --> 00:03:11,240
Young Master Bai.

17
00:03:11,241 --> 00:03:13,160
Didn't expect it to be you in here.

18
00:03:13,759 --> 00:03:14,520
You know him?

19
00:03:14,759 --> 00:03:15,559
I do.

20
00:03:15,759 --> 00:03:17,479
Met him at one of Shi Lihua's parties.

21
00:03:17,759 --> 00:03:18,999
What do you two want?

22
00:03:19,000 --> 00:03:20,760
You barge in and start
smashing things, huh?

23
00:03:24,119 --> 00:03:25,959
What do we want with you?

24
00:03:25,960 --> 00:03:27,320
You know exactly why.

25
00:03:28,039 --> 00:03:29,799
Since I could find you today

26
00:03:29,800 --> 00:03:31,880
I came prepared.

27
00:03:32,360 --> 00:03:34,360
If you don't mind an audience,

28
00:03:35,080 --> 00:03:36,279
then I don't either.

29
00:03:36,520 --> 00:03:37,440
Fine.

30
00:03:37,441 --> 00:03:38,679
Let's talk.

31
00:03:39,240 --> 00:03:40,999
Everybody get the hell out,

32
00:03:41,000 --> 00:03:42,360
I've got real business to discuss.

33
00:03:42,679 --> 00:03:44,398
Go warm up another room

34
00:03:44,399 --> 00:03:45,440
I'll be there later.

35
00:03:45,839 --> 00:03:46,999
We'll be waiting, Young Master Bai.

36
00:03:47,000 --> 00:03:47,800
We'll be waiting, bro.
We'll head over first.

37
00:03:52,679 --> 00:03:53,838
All right

38
00:03:53,839 --> 00:03:54,839
talk.

39
00:03:55,399 --> 00:03:56,719
Young Master Bai.

40
00:03:56,720 --> 00:03:58,400
Even though we don't know each other well,

41
00:03:58,960 --> 00:04:00,960
we do have Shi Lihua in common.

42
00:04:01,279 --> 00:04:02,319
So.

43
00:04:02,320 --> 00:04:03,800
If you've got anything to say.

44
00:04:04,119 --> 00:04:05,800
Think it over carefully.

45
00:04:05,960 --> 00:04:07,478
And don't play coy.

46
00:04:07,479 --> 00:04:08,720
President Fan, right?

47
00:04:08,800 --> 00:04:12,600
What relationship do you have with
this gentleman who wants to talk to me?

48
00:04:12,919 --> 00:04:13,919
He's my friend.

49
00:04:15,000 --> 00:04:16,079
Oh—friends.

50
00:04:18,959 --> 00:04:20,078
Young Master Bai.

51
00:04:20,079 --> 00:04:21,238
Today

52
00:04:21,239 --> 00:04:23,239
I'm here for an explanation.

53
00:04:24,279 --> 00:04:25,279
With this chemistry...

54
00:04:25,760 --> 00:04:27,958
If I hadn't personally got him to the bed

55
00:04:27,959 --> 00:04:29,679
I might believe they're just “friends”.

56
00:04:30,119 --> 00:04:31,359
Real good at pretending.

57
00:04:32,160 --> 00:04:34,519
What are you on about guy?

58
00:04:34,679 --> 00:04:35,798
What “explanation”?

59
00:04:35,799 --> 00:04:36,999
I don't follow.

60
00:04:37,000 --> 00:04:37,640
That tracks.

61
00:04:37,641 --> 00:04:40,000
You've done so many filthy things.

62
00:04:40,079 --> 00:04:42,720
You can't keep track of them all.

63
00:04:43,799 --> 00:04:45,079
Let me jog your memory...

64
00:04:45,600 --> 00:04:47,160
last Thursday night.

65
00:04:47,839 --> 00:04:50,279
The Qiyue Hotel parking lot.

66
00:04:56,559 --> 00:04:58,760
Then tell me...

67
00:04:58,920 --> 00:05:01,238
that night.

68
00:05:01,239 --> 00:05:03,079
What exactly did I do to you?

69
00:05:03,119 --> 00:05:04,439
What the hell are you looking at?

70
00:05:05,000 --> 00:05:06,920
I wouldn't be here without proof.

71
00:05:07,359 --> 00:05:08,359
Young Master Bai.

72
00:05:08,839 --> 00:05:10,679
If you've got no explanation

73
00:05:10,959 --> 00:05:13,119
I'll assume it was you.

74
00:05:13,320 --> 00:05:17,839
Then today, I'm afriad
I'm here to settle the score.

75
00:05:18,079 --> 00:05:20,278
How do you plan on doing that?

76
00:05:20,279 --> 00:05:21,320
Simple.

77
00:05:23,559 --> 00:05:24,880
An eye for an eye.

78
00:05:25,480 --> 00:05:26,880
Whatever you did to me

79
00:05:27,279 --> 00:05:29,119
I'll return in kind.

80
00:05:30,640 --> 00:05:31,719
Young Master Bai.

81
00:05:31,720 --> 00:05:33,078
Where do we start undressing you?

82
00:05:33,079 --> 00:05:34,238
Screw you!

83
00:05:34,239 --> 00:05:34,760
I'm straight.
Young Master Bai.

84
00:05:35,799 --> 00:05:37,320
Watch your mouth.

85
00:05:38,119 --> 00:05:39,640
Your phone's been ringing.

86
00:05:40,239 --> 00:05:41,880
Take the call first.

87
00:05:42,200 --> 00:05:43,879
Calm down.

88
00:05:43,880 --> 00:05:45,079
Then we'll talk.

89
00:05:45,279 --> 00:05:46,119
Fan Xiao.

90
00:05:46,120 --> 00:05:47,720
How the hell are we supposed to talk?

91
00:05:47,959 --> 00:05:48,959
No rush.

92
00:05:49,880 --> 00:05:51,760
Take the call first.

93
00:05:51,920 --> 00:05:53,439
Sit.

94
00:05:53,440 --> 00:05:54,959
We'll talk slowly.

95
00:05:58,959 --> 00:06:00,040
Hello.

96
00:06:02,920 --> 00:06:03,959
Okay.

97
00:06:07,519 --> 00:06:08,519
Fine—I admit it

98
00:06:08,520 --> 00:06:09,600
I did it.

99
00:06:10,600 --> 00:06:11,720
Why?

100
00:06:13,119 --> 00:06:14,959
Why the hell do you think?

101
00:06:15,079 --> 00:06:15,839
I took a little something.

102
00:06:15,840 --> 00:06:16,959
Got revved up.

103
00:06:17,200 --> 00:06:18,559
No one was around.

104
00:06:19,160 --> 00:06:20,398
You looked decent.

105
00:06:20,399 --> 00:06:21,279
Good enough.

106
00:06:21,280 --> 00:06:22,759
You carry ether on you?

107
00:06:22,760 --> 00:06:23,640
And what if I do?

108
00:06:23,641 --> 00:06:25,160
My hobby—problem?

109
00:06:25,799 --> 00:06:26,559
Just say it.
How much?

110
00:06:27,880 --> 00:06:29,160
I don't want your money.

111
00:06:36,959 --> 00:06:38,079
Then what do you want?

112
00:06:38,239 --> 00:06:39,479
What you just said won't fly.

113
00:06:39,480 --> 00:06:40,399
Relax

114
00:06:40,400 --> 00:06:42,136
I can't bring myself to
put my mouth on you.

115
00:06:42,160 --> 00:06:43,518
Give me ten minutes to beat you.

116
00:06:43,519 --> 00:06:44,880
We call it even.

117
00:06:46,150 --> 00:06:47,150
Fuck!

118
00:06:47,279 --> 00:06:48,119
You dare lay a hand on me?

119
00:06:48,120 --> 00:06:49,559
I'll kill you today!

120
00:06:53,880 --> 00:06:55,159
Dare hit me, huh?

121
00:06:55,160 --> 00:06:56,760
I'll bust your head for free today.

122
00:07:01,079 --> 00:07:02,238
You dare swing that at him?

123
00:07:02,239 --> 00:07:03,518
Say the word if you want to die.

124
00:07:03,519 --> 00:07:04,040
Fan Xiao.
Don't...

125
00:07:04,519 --> 00:07:05,519
Don't worry.

126
00:07:05,959 --> 00:07:06,959
I won't take his life

127
00:07:08,000 --> 00:07:09,279
I'll handle the dirty work.

128
00:07:10,799 --> 00:07:12,278
Ten minutes.

129
00:07:12,279 --> 00:07:13,399
Time me.

130
00:07:16,600 --> 00:07:17,200
Fan Xiao.

131
00:07:17,201 --> 00:07:18,359
You're really doing this...

132
00:07:18,880 --> 00:07:21,040
If we're doing the play, do the whole act.

133
00:07:21,279 --> 00:07:22,546
Thanks for your cooperation,
Young Master Bai.

134
00:07:22,570 --> 00:07:23,150
Bastard.

135
00:07:23,519 --> 00:07:24,919
I'm done playing,

136
00:07:24,920 --> 00:07:26,279
I'll spill everything.

137
00:07:30,519 --> 00:07:31,559
Not even for Anna?

138
00:07:37,040 --> 00:07:39,880
Shi Lihua said you could
have her sleep with me.

139
00:07:40,079 --> 00:07:41,079
Is that for real?

140
00:07:41,640 --> 00:07:43,040
She's a beauty queen after all

141
00:07:43,720 --> 00:07:45,720
I'll have her come out
to drink with you first.

142
00:07:46,079 --> 00:07:49,679
Whether you can take her home
or not depends on your skills.

143
00:07:51,640 --> 00:07:52,880
Then hurry—hit me quick.

144
00:07:54,040 --> 00:07:57,040
I'll stick to exposed skin then.

145
00:07:57,399 --> 00:07:58,678
The effect is better.

146
00:07:58,679 --> 00:08:00,040
And you'll suffer less.

147
00:08:03,160 --> 00:08:04,160
Apologies in advance.

148
00:08:13,119 --> 00:08:14,200
No more.

149
00:08:14,600 --> 00:08:16,640
Any more and I'll see the King of Hell.

150
00:08:17,000 --> 00:08:18,040
Fine.

151
00:08:19,160 --> 00:08:20,399
One last hit.

152
00:08:21,119 --> 00:08:22,278
Remember in a minute.

153
00:08:22,279 --> 00:08:23,798
Scream louder.

154
00:08:23,799 --> 00:08:24,799
Fan Xiao.

155
00:08:24,880 --> 00:08:25,880
What are you doing?

156
00:08:27,200 --> 00:08:29,640
Our Bai family isn't made up of easy
targets.

157
00:08:32,840 --> 00:08:34,200
Just scream.

158
00:08:48,880 --> 00:08:50,799
What are you doing?

159
00:08:51,359 --> 00:08:52,839
Tell me...

160
00:08:52,840 --> 00:08:55,158
Will the person outside feel sorry?

161
00:08:55,159 --> 00:08:56,159
I…

162
00:08:56,799 --> 00:08:58,840
I don't know.

163
00:08:59,479 --> 00:09:00,519
Young Master Bai.

164
00:09:00,520 --> 00:09:02,359
You must take the fall for this.

165
00:09:02,679 --> 00:09:03,840
Remember what I said.

166
00:09:04,119 --> 00:09:06,119
Offend anyone but not Fan Xiao.

167
00:09:06,400 --> 00:09:07,880
He'll smile and play you to death.

168
00:09:09,000 --> 00:09:13,640
I should ask him for something good.

169
00:09:17,119 --> 00:09:19,359
Thanks for your hard
work, Young Master Bai.

170
00:09:43,559 --> 00:09:44,640
Let's go.

171
00:09:48,640 --> 00:09:50,400
Wait—your hand.

172
00:09:50,640 --> 00:09:52,079
It's nothing

173
00:09:52,080 --> 00:09:54,119
I just banged it when I
worked that punk over.

174
00:09:54,640 --> 00:09:56,200
Just hit the wall by accident.

175
00:09:56,599 --> 00:09:57,359
No.

176
00:09:57,360 --> 00:09:58,440
To the hospital.

177
00:10:09,000 --> 00:10:12,200
(Episode 4)

178
00:10:15,960 --> 00:10:18,119
Welcome, Director You to my humble abode.

179
00:10:19,760 --> 00:10:21,199
Your right hand just got put in a splint.

180
00:10:21,200 --> 00:10:22,200
Don't move it.

181
00:10:22,479 --> 00:10:24,038
Whatever you have trouble doing, just tell
me.

182
00:10:24,039 --> 00:10:25,039
I'll help you.

183
00:10:27,080 --> 00:10:28,239
It's really nothing

184
00:10:29,799 --> 00:10:30,799
I'll do it.

185
00:10:31,200 --> 00:10:32,719
You're a grown man—don't be stubborn.

186
00:10:33,599 --> 00:10:34,599
Slow down.

187
00:10:34,679 --> 00:10:35,559
Your metacarpal's fractured.

188
00:10:35,560 --> 00:10:36,919
And you say “no big deal”.

189
00:10:38,960 --> 00:10:43,280
The doctor also said if this doesn't
heal right, you'll have longterm problems.

190
00:10:48,719 --> 00:10:49,200
Fan Xiao.

191
00:10:49,201 --> 00:10:50,759
You've been in Thailand a while.

192
00:10:50,760 --> 00:10:52,640
Why does your place still look like a
showroom?

193
00:10:53,640 --> 00:10:55,359
I'm mostly at the office

194
00:10:55,471 --> 00:10:57,551
I live here for the quietness.

195
00:10:58,479 --> 00:10:59,960
You can check the terrace.

196
00:11:00,479 --> 00:11:01,640
The view's great.

197
00:11:09,960 --> 00:11:11,358
At night.

198
00:11:11,359 --> 00:11:13,000
You can only see the mountain outlines.

199
00:11:13,359 --> 00:11:15,880
In the daytime, especially after rain.

200
00:11:16,960 --> 00:11:17,960
It's beautiful.

201
00:11:26,960 --> 00:11:31,960
If there's anything that you can't do easily
one-handed before you sleep, just let me know.

202
00:11:37,960 --> 00:11:39,719
This collar's a little tight.

203
00:11:40,080 --> 00:11:42,959
Do you mind giving me a hand, Director You?

204
00:11:42,960 --> 00:11:44,798
It's not like both hands are useless.

205
00:11:44,799 --> 00:11:45,880
Use your left.

206
00:11:48,840 --> 00:11:49,840
Useless.

207
00:11:51,880 --> 00:11:52,999
Don't move your right hand.

208
00:11:53,000 --> 00:11:54,000
Come here.

209
00:12:02,679 --> 00:12:03,679
Come.

210
00:12:04,760 --> 00:12:05,760
Slow down.

211
00:12:05,880 --> 00:12:07,440
Director You really does care about me.

212
00:12:08,119 --> 00:12:09,119
Zip it.

213
00:12:10,200 --> 00:12:11,200
Chin down.

214
00:12:46,640 --> 00:12:48,039
What are you doing?

215
00:12:52,400 --> 00:12:54,480
The curtain remote,
I've been looking for it forever.

216
00:12:54,599 --> 00:12:56,320
It was wedged in the sofa behind you.

217
00:12:59,960 --> 00:13:01,478
Director You.

218
00:13:01,479 --> 00:13:02,960
There are two buttons left.

219
00:13:09,280 --> 00:13:10,280
There.

220
00:13:13,400 --> 00:13:14,440
I'll change into a robe.

221
00:13:29,520 --> 00:13:30,239
Fan Xiao

222
00:13:30,240 --> 00:13:32,598
I think the person who molested me

223
00:13:32,599 --> 00:13:33,999
wasn't Bai Pengyu.

224
00:13:34,000 --> 00:13:35,000
How so?

225
00:13:36,320 --> 00:13:37,598
Last time I deliberately said

226
00:13:37,599 --> 00:13:38,999
“an eye for an eye”

227
00:13:39,000 --> 00:13:40,000
to test him.

228
00:13:41,599 --> 00:13:43,760
But he clearly hates men.

229
00:13:43,880 --> 00:13:45,358
He took something

230
00:13:45,359 --> 00:13:46,280
and drank.

231
00:13:46,281 --> 00:13:48,798
When you're that out of it,

232
00:13:48,799 --> 00:13:50,080
you don't care.

233
00:13:52,039 --> 00:13:53,798
You shouldn't drink on meds.

234
00:13:53,799 --> 00:13:54,839
I know.

235
00:13:54,840 --> 00:13:55,840
This is for you...

236
00:13:56,320 --> 00:13:57,718
have a little to relax

237
00:13:57,719 --> 00:13:59,358
and sleep.

238
00:13:59,359 --> 00:14:00,719
If you're not at ease,

239
00:14:00,799 --> 00:14:01,799
we'll keep digging.

240
00:14:02,320 --> 00:14:03,840
The lady boss who poured you drinks...

241
00:14:03,960 --> 00:14:05,000
I checked.

242
00:14:05,159 --> 00:14:06,080
It wasn't her.
We'll see.

243
00:14:08,840 --> 00:14:09,880
Either way,

244
00:14:10,159 --> 00:14:11,656
thanks, Fan Xiao.

245
00:14:13,080 --> 00:14:14,520
Honestly…

246
00:14:14,880 --> 00:14:16,080
from childhood to now,

247
00:14:18,520 --> 00:14:20,280
few people have ever
protected me like this.

248
00:14:21,919 --> 00:14:22,919
What?

249
00:14:24,640 --> 00:14:25,640
Do you know

250
00:14:25,641 --> 00:14:26,918
what the women at our company

251
00:14:26,919 --> 00:14:28,080
say about you?

252
00:14:28,200 --> 00:14:29,239
What do they say?

253
00:14:30,479 --> 00:14:31,639
They say

254
00:14:31,640 --> 00:14:34,479
you're the brooding, scheming male lead...

255
00:14:34,679 --> 00:14:36,558
anyone you latch onto,

256
00:14:36,559 --> 00:14:38,239
things always end poorly for them.

257
00:14:39,520 --> 00:14:40,479
If they knew

258
00:14:40,480 --> 00:14:42,320
you're this childish and clingy,

259
00:14:42,840 --> 00:14:44,280
what would they think?

260
00:14:52,359 --> 00:14:53,359
You Shulang.

261
00:14:53,840 --> 00:14:55,640
I don't care what they think.

262
00:14:56,960 --> 00:14:58,440
I only want to know

263
00:14:58,880 --> 00:15:00,159
what you think.

264
00:15:15,200 --> 00:15:16,358
It's late.

265
00:15:16,359 --> 00:15:17,559
You won't get a cab here.

266
00:15:18,239 --> 00:15:19,359
Just don't go back.

267
00:15:20,400 --> 00:15:21,719
I can't drive with this hand.

268
00:15:22,200 --> 00:15:24,280
Tomorrow I'll trouble
you to take me to work.

269
00:15:25,080 --> 00:15:26,679
The guest room has its own bath.

270
00:15:26,919 --> 00:15:27,999
The bedding's new.

271
00:15:28,000 --> 00:15:29,000
No one's used it.

272
00:15:29,359 --> 00:15:30,639
Treat it like a hotel

273
00:15:30,640 --> 00:15:31,640
for the night.

274
00:15:36,039 --> 00:15:38,079
Keep the hand dry after you go home.

275
00:15:38,080 --> 00:15:39,559
I'll prescribe antibiotics.

276
00:15:39,960 --> 00:15:41,759
You may run a fever tonight,

277
00:15:41,760 --> 00:15:42,760
keep an eye on it.

278
00:15:58,119 --> 00:15:59,119
Fan Xiao.

279
00:15:59,559 --> 00:16:00,559
Fan Xiao.

280
00:16:08,520 --> 00:16:09,520
Fan Xiao.

281
00:16:10,400 --> 00:16:11,679
Are you feeling unwell?

282
00:16:12,200 --> 00:16:13,200
Shulang.

283
00:16:14,599 --> 00:16:15,919
I am actually feeling unwell.

284
00:16:22,760 --> 00:16:24,719
You said you'd help me.

285
00:16:30,640 --> 00:16:31,640
Fan Xiao.

286
00:16:35,599 --> 00:16:37,039
I'm just asking a favor.

287
00:16:37,559 --> 00:16:39,199
No need to throw a punch if you disagree.

