It's not teasing,
I can vouch for it.

577
00:31:47,160 --> 00:31:49,198
Every time your name
comes up, they get so excited

578
00:31:49,199 --> 00:31:51,280
the boss has to cough to shut them up.

579
00:31:51,520 --> 00:31:52,598
Can't blame them.

580
00:31:52,599 --> 00:31:54,319
You're handsome and attentive.

581
00:31:54,599 --> 00:31:56,598
It's a good thing you're here
with President Fan injured...

582
00:31:56,599 --> 00:31:57,640
otherwise,

583
00:31:57,800 --> 00:31:59,718
none of us know him that well,

584
00:31:59,719 --> 00:32:00,958
and we wouldn't know how to look after him.

585
00:32:00,959 --> 00:32:02,079
It's just work.

586
00:32:02,920 --> 00:32:03,920
Tell you what...

587
00:32:04,000 --> 00:32:05,239
you two stroll awhile.

588
00:32:05,599 --> 00:32:07,400
He barely ate today.

589
00:32:07,760 --> 00:32:08,799
I'll bring him some food

590
00:32:08,800 --> 00:32:09,800
and go find him.

591
00:32:10,439 --> 00:32:11,800
Sure, sure.

592
00:32:12,079 --> 00:32:13,079
See you later.

593
00:32:19,479 --> 00:32:20,479
Don't turn on the light.

594
00:32:21,199 --> 00:32:22,199
Please

595
00:32:22,880 --> 00:32:23,880
don't turn it on.

596
00:32:24,160 --> 00:32:25,160
Fan Xiao?

597
00:32:34,719 --> 00:32:35,719
What's wrong, Fan Xiao?

598
00:32:37,920 --> 00:32:38,959
Let me hold you

599
00:32:39,280 --> 00:32:40,239
just for a minute.
It's okay.

600
00:32:41,680 --> 00:32:42,680
I'm here.

601
00:32:43,199 --> 00:32:45,358
I haven't been to the sea in a long time.

602
00:32:45,359 --> 00:32:46,599
I'll get you some water.

603
00:32:46,965 --> 00:32:48,006
Pour me a real drink.

604
00:32:49,520 --> 00:32:50,520
Okay.

605
00:33:08,719 --> 00:33:09,719
You know

606
00:33:10,839 --> 00:33:13,319
the tsunami that killed over three
hundred thousand people?

607
00:33:13,520 --> 00:33:14,520
You mean

608
00:33:15,479 --> 00:33:16,479
decades ago,

609
00:33:17,160 --> 00:33:18,359
the one in Indonesia?

610
00:33:19,280 --> 00:33:21,319
My family was vacationing on an island.

611
00:33:21,880 --> 00:33:23,800
Minutes before it hit,

612
00:33:25,160 --> 00:33:27,160
I was eating sticky rice,

613
00:33:27,959 --> 00:33:29,400
wrapped in lotus leaf.

614
00:33:30,520 --> 00:33:32,000
For years after,

615
00:33:32,479 --> 00:33:34,199
every nightmare

616
00:33:35,479 --> 00:33:37,199
carried that smell.

617
00:33:38,040 --> 00:33:39,920
I just smelled it again.

618
00:33:40,839 --> 00:33:42,640
I was back there...

619
00:33:42,760 --> 00:33:44,640
swaddled in my mother's arms,

620
00:33:46,239 --> 00:33:47,719
shaking with fear.

621
00:33:48,800 --> 00:33:49,800
Sorry...

622
00:33:50,640 --> 00:33:51,839
did I scare you?

623
00:33:54,479 --> 00:33:55,479
It's okay.

624
00:33:57,920 --> 00:33:58,920
Let me...

625
00:34:01,719 --> 00:34:02,719
Shulang...

626
00:34:03,319 --> 00:34:04,680
if it were you,

627
00:34:04,880 --> 00:34:06,280
would you reach out

628
00:34:07,839 --> 00:34:08,959
to protect someone?

629
00:34:10,919 --> 00:34:11,919
I'm not sure.

630
00:34:13,879 --> 00:34:15,560
In life-or-death situations,

631
00:34:15,760 --> 00:34:17,800
no one knows how they'll act.

632
00:34:18,719 --> 00:34:20,679
What if it's your spouse and child?

633
00:34:24,479 --> 00:34:25,760
I wouldn't leave them.

634
00:34:30,320 --> 00:34:31,320
Director You...

635
00:34:31,879 --> 00:34:33,479
I knew you were a good man.

636
00:34:36,600 --> 00:34:37,719
At least

637
00:34:40,479 --> 00:34:41,239
you and your mother

638
00:34:41,240 --> 00:34:42,399
made it out.

639
00:34:52,159 --> 00:34:53,239
She died.

640
00:34:55,000 --> 00:34:55,959
Mom,

641
00:34:55,960 --> 00:34:58,079
the water is rising.

642
00:34:58,080 --> 00:34:59,600
Mom's got you.

643
00:35:01,560 --> 00:35:02,320
Mom...
don't be afraid.

644
00:35:03,240 --> 00:35:05,239
Are we going to die?

645
00:35:05,280 --> 00:35:06,239
No, Xiao-xiao.
I'm here.

646
00:35:08,199 --> 00:35:09,199
It will pass.

647
00:35:09,239 --> 00:35:10,239
It'll be okay.

648
00:35:10,520 --> 00:35:12,800
Mom, I'm scared.

649
00:35:14,959 --> 00:35:16,360
I've got matches.

650
00:35:21,600 --> 00:35:22,239
Hold these.

651
00:35:22,240 --> 00:35:23,360
And this too.

652
00:35:23,520 --> 00:35:24,600
If you get too scared,

653
00:35:24,639 --> 00:35:25,520
we'll light another.

654
00:35:25,521 --> 00:35:27,919
In the end she used all her strength

655
00:35:29,479 --> 00:35:31,839
to pile everything in the room

656
00:35:31,840 --> 00:35:33,199
into a corner

657
00:35:33,320 --> 00:35:34,719
and had me stand on it.

658
00:35:36,600 --> 00:35:38,238
I watched her

659
00:35:38,239 --> 00:35:40,360
sink inch by inch.

660
00:35:40,879 --> 00:35:43,000
The last thing she said to me...

661
00:35:43,239 --> 00:35:44,360
Xiao-xiao,

662
00:35:44,600 --> 00:35:45,679
you have to live.

663
00:35:46,080 --> 00:35:47,559
Is living so hard?

664
00:35:47,560 --> 00:35:49,399
Living is truly painful.

665
00:35:53,320 --> 00:35:54,719
My mother died...

666
00:35:55,320 --> 00:35:57,040
right in front of me.

667
00:35:58,199 --> 00:35:59,679
It was so dark.

668
00:36:00,040 --> 00:36:01,679
I had only a box of matches.

669
00:36:04,159 --> 00:36:05,159
Later,

670
00:36:07,159 --> 00:36:08,760
my matches ran out.

671
00:36:09,080 --> 00:36:10,600
I couldn't see her.

672
00:36:12,560 --> 00:36:13,560
Fan Xiao…

673
00:36:17,360 --> 00:36:17,959
Mom…

674
00:36:18,280 --> 00:36:19,600
why did you

675
00:36:20,840 --> 00:36:23,280
keep telling me to live?

676
00:36:24,199 --> 00:36:25,959
My matches are gone.

677
00:36:27,840 --> 00:36:29,760
I want to be with you.

678
00:36:30,879 --> 00:36:32,840
This world is too dark.

679
00:36:34,560 --> 00:36:35,800
I hate them.

680
00:36:36,320 --> 00:36:37,840
I hate everyone.

681
00:36:38,760 --> 00:36:40,479
They should've all drowned with you.

682
00:36:42,159 --> 00:36:43,159
Fan Xiao...

683
00:36:43,719 --> 00:36:44,719
Fan Xiao...

684
00:36:45,120 --> 00:36:46,120
calm down.

685
00:36:46,600 --> 00:36:47,600
Calm down.

686
00:36:48,120 --> 00:36:49,679
That tsunami has long past.

687
00:36:49,840 --> 00:36:51,199
It's over now.

688
00:36:54,080 --> 00:36:55,080
Shulang?

689
00:36:55,159 --> 00:36:56,159
It's me.

690
00:36:56,560 --> 00:36:57,560
I'm here.

691
00:36:59,800 --> 00:37:01,000
Do you know

692
00:37:02,080 --> 00:37:03,080
who I hate most right now?

693
00:37:03,081 --> 00:37:04,159
You.

694
00:37:04,760 --> 00:37:05,760
Fan Xiao...

695
00:37:05,959 --> 00:37:06,959
breathe—calm down.

696
00:37:07,239 --> 00:37:08,000
Calm down.

697
00:37:08,199 --> 00:37:10,000
Who do you think you are

698
00:37:10,600 --> 00:37:12,479
to decide others' lives and deaths?

699
00:37:13,479 --> 00:37:14,800
Who do you think you are...

700
00:37:15,040 --> 00:37:16,919
a bodhisattva who saves all?

701
00:37:18,080 --> 00:37:19,080
Fan Xiao...

702
00:37:19,239 --> 00:37:20,280
calm down.

703
00:37:21,280 --> 00:37:22,840
Then save me.

704
00:37:41,439 --> 00:37:42,439
Fan Xiao...

705
00:37:46,560 --> 00:37:47,959
Sorry.

706
00:37:49,800 --> 00:37:50,439
I just...

707
00:37:50,520 --> 00:37:51,520
It's okay.

708
00:37:52,120 --> 00:37:53,120
I get it...

709
00:37:54,320 --> 00:37:55,320
trauma response.

710
00:37:59,639 --> 00:38:01,119
Last time I got drunk

711
00:38:01,120 --> 00:38:02,800
and crossed a line.

712
00:38:03,840 --> 00:38:05,040
This time you were triggered.

713
00:38:06,000 --> 00:38:07,000
We're even.

714
00:38:07,560 --> 00:38:08,719
Let's not bring it up again.

715
00:38:11,800 --> 00:38:12,800
You kissed me.

716
00:38:14,159 --> 00:38:15,159
I kissed you.

717
00:38:15,479 --> 00:38:16,520
It's done with.

718
00:38:20,040 --> 00:38:21,599
The udon I packed

719
00:38:21,600 --> 00:38:22,600
is probably soggy.

720
00:38:23,280 --> 00:38:24,280
I'll buy another.

721
00:38:25,040 --> 00:38:26,040
Shulang...

722
00:38:27,639 --> 00:38:28,520
do you know why

723
00:38:28,521 --> 00:38:30,600
I put your name

724
00:38:31,040 --> 00:38:32,320
onto the travel list?

725
00:38:32,679 --> 00:38:33,679
No.

726
00:38:34,239 --> 00:38:35,120
Because I hope

727
00:38:35,121 --> 00:38:36,959
that when I'm afraid, you'll be there.

728
00:38:37,719 --> 00:38:38,719
When you're there,

729
00:38:40,320 --> 00:38:41,760
I'm calmer.

730
00:38:56,639 --> 00:38:57,639
What?

731
00:38:57,840 --> 00:38:59,639
You actually went to the coast?

732
00:38:59,959 --> 00:39:01,320
Aren't you afraid of a relapse?

733
00:39:02,000 --> 00:39:03,000
Already had one.

734
00:39:05,320 --> 00:39:07,159
Then why do you sound normal?

735
00:39:08,840 --> 00:39:09,840
Director You is here.

736
00:39:10,120 --> 00:39:11,120
Meaning?

737
00:39:11,320 --> 00:39:12,959
I can't run forever.

738
00:39:14,600 --> 00:39:15,239
If I'm going to try

739
00:39:15,240 --> 00:39:16,600
to take a step forward,

740
00:39:17,560 --> 00:39:18,199
might as well

741
00:39:18,200 --> 00:39:19,719
milk a little pity in front of him.

742
00:39:20,000 --> 00:39:21,600
That works?

743
00:39:21,959 --> 00:39:22,959
You...

744
00:39:23,320 --> 00:39:24,320
So annoying.

745
00:39:24,600 --> 00:39:28,719
Distinguished business
representatives, please take a short break.

746
00:39:28,760 --> 00:39:31,600
Our forum will officially begin in ten
minutes.

747
00:39:34,879 --> 00:39:35,719
Excuse me...

748
00:39:35,720 --> 00:39:38,159
could you please help us adjust our seats?

749
00:39:38,360 --> 00:39:41,320
I need a seat that's not by the window.

750
00:39:41,639 --> 00:39:42,000
All right.

751
00:39:42,001 --> 00:39:43,040
Let me coordinate it.

752
00:39:43,399 --> 00:39:44,399
Thank you.

753
00:39:49,479 --> 00:39:50,638
Excuse me...

754
00:39:50,639 --> 00:39:52,479
the sea breeze is so noisy.

755
00:39:52,600 --> 00:39:54,320
Would you mind closing the window?

756
00:39:59,120 --> 00:40:00,239
First of all,

757
00:40:00,639 --> 00:40:01,360
I'm very happy

758
00:40:01,399 --> 00:40:04,280
to attend this WS-hosted summit.

759
00:40:05,719 --> 00:40:06,958
Here,

760
00:40:06,959 --> 00:40:09,399
I see many old friends.

761
00:40:09,800 --> 00:40:11,719
Thank you all for coming.

762
00:40:13,280 --> 00:40:21,120
This forum is, domestically, and even in
international medical exchange, or in technology,

763
00:40:21,639 --> 00:40:23,359
by all acounts is top-tier...

764
00:40:23,360 --> 00:40:25,399
This expert is very forward-thinking,

765
00:40:25,879 --> 00:40:26,919
with a global vision.

766
00:40:27,854 --> 00:40:28,495
Listen up.

767
00:40:28,520 --> 00:40:31,960
We have received strong support
from investors at home and abroad...

768
00:40:35,919 --> 00:40:39,679
Well, thanks to the experts
for their wonderful speeches.

769
00:40:40,000 --> 00:40:42,320
That's all for today's theme forum.

770
00:40:42,719 --> 00:40:45,560
Everyone can go to the
restaurant to enjoy dinner.

771
00:40:45,719 --> 00:40:46,719
Thank you, everybody.
See you tomorrow.

772
00:40:47,919 --> 00:40:48,600
Let's go.

773
00:40:48,601 --> 00:40:49,679
I've already ordered.

774
00:40:50,199 --> 00:40:51,319
Let's eat back at the hotel.

775
00:40:52,399 --> 00:40:53,399
Shulang...

776
00:40:56,159 --> 00:40:56,679
What is it?

777
00:40:56,800 --> 00:40:58,320
Walk the beach with me.

778
00:41:01,959 --> 00:41:02,800
You sure?
It'll be dark soon.

779
00:41:03,840 --> 00:41:05,040
You may not see the water,

780
00:41:05,959 --> 00:41:07,600
but the waves will still...

781
00:41:08,080 --> 00:41:09,080
I want

782
00:41:10,040 --> 00:41:11,040
to try.

783
00:41:28,760 --> 00:41:29,320
Fan Xiao...

784
00:41:29,719 --> 00:41:30,719
Fan Xiao...

785
00:41:30,879 --> 00:41:31,879
come back.

786
00:41:32,360 --> 00:41:33,159
Fan Xiao...
stop.

787
00:41:36,120 --> 00:41:37,120
What...

788
00:41:37,159 --> 00:41:38,080
afraid I'll kill myself?

789
00:41:38,081 --> 00:41:39,479
Walk back, Fan Xiao.

790
00:41:39,679 --> 00:41:40,736
If you want exposure therapy

791
00:41:40,760 --> 00:41:42,080
you can't rush it.

792
00:41:51,199 --> 00:41:52,199
So...

793
00:41:54,239 --> 00:41:56,239
after the accident you
never came back to the sea?

794
00:41:57,959 --> 00:41:58,959
Afterward

795
00:41:59,199 --> 00:42:01,199
I did therapy on-and-off for years.

796
00:42:02,919 --> 00:42:04,879
As an adult I thought I could face it,

797
00:42:06,040 --> 00:42:07,280
so I went to Phuket.

798
00:42:07,919 --> 00:42:09,199
I didn't even see the ocean...

799
00:42:09,919 --> 00:42:11,559
just hearing it

800
00:42:11,560 --> 00:42:12,600
sent me over the edge.

801
00:42:12,959 --> 00:42:14,079
Later

802
00:42:14,080 --> 00:42:15,560
I tried desensitization again,

803
00:42:16,719 --> 00:42:17,879
but it didn't help.

804
00:42:18,159 --> 00:42:19,199
Slowly...

805
00:42:20,959 --> 00:42:23,479
I got tired, I couldn't lose control again.

806
00:42:24,080 --> 00:42:26,080
I didn't want to face the
nightmare over and over.

807
00:42:26,959 --> 00:42:28,600
In the end

808
00:42:28,840 --> 00:42:30,520
I could only give up

809
00:42:31,080 --> 00:42:32,120
and run.

810
00:42:33,040 --> 00:42:34,040
Like a coward.

811
00:42:34,959 --> 00:42:36,040
Will you laugh at me?

812
00:42:36,239 --> 00:42:37,239
Fan Xiao...

813
00:42:37,679 --> 00:42:38,679
it's not like that.

814
00:42:40,520 --> 00:42:42,679
Everyone has something they can't face.

815
00:42:42,760 --> 00:42:43,760
You too?

816
00:42:44,879 --> 00:42:45,879
I'm afraid to swim.

817
00:42:46,600 --> 00:42:48,119
I actually used to be good at it.

818
00:42:48,120 --> 00:42:49,360
I was very good at swimming.

819
00:42:52,080 --> 00:42:53,319
Back then,

820
00:42:53,320 --> 00:42:54,320
we were poor.

821
00:42:55,320 --> 00:42:56,878
We boys went to the river

822
00:42:56,879 --> 00:42:58,079
to set fish traps.

823
00:42:58,080 --> 00:42:59,760
Another kid and I swam well,

824
00:43:00,879 --> 00:43:02,320
we dared to set traps deep.

825
00:43:02,679 --> 00:43:04,679
We caught more fish than the others.

826
00:43:05,760 --> 00:43:06,760
But slowly

827
00:43:08,280 --> 00:43:10,080
he saw me as a rival,

828
00:43:10,966 --> 00:43:12,246
he started to resent me,

829
00:43:12,679 --> 00:43:14,399
and bullied my younger brother.

830
00:43:15,159 --> 00:43:17,199
Once he set the trap too deep.

831
00:43:18,000 --> 00:43:19,958
When he dove to get it,

832
00:43:19,959 --> 00:43:21,120
his legs got tangled.

833
00:43:21,760 --> 00:43:22,760
You saved him?

834
00:43:25,760 --> 00:43:26,719
Yes.
I saved him,

835
00:43:28,800 --> 00:43:30,639
but he almost dragged me down with him.

836
00:43:31,639 --> 00:43:33,000
He panicked,

837
00:43:33,399 --> 00:43:35,000
clutched my arms and legs.

838
00:43:35,520 --> 00:43:37,478
Then a gulp of water knocked him out,

839
00:43:37,479 --> 00:43:38,719
and I dragged him ashore.

840
00:43:40,719 --> 00:43:41,560
Want a cigarette?

841
00:43:41,719 --> 00:43:42,719
No.

842
00:43:43,280 --> 00:43:44,280
No smoking on the beach.

843
00:43:45,199 --> 00:43:47,360
But after he came to,

844
00:43:47,879 --> 00:43:49,280
he accused me

845
00:43:49,879 --> 00:43:51,560
of diving in to steal his fish.

846
00:43:52,800 --> 00:43:54,039
A year later,

847
00:43:54,040 --> 00:43:55,239
he did it again.

848
00:43:57,000 --> 00:43:58,959
But that time I hesitated.

849
00:44:00,959 --> 00:44:03,399
I stood on shore watching
him thrash and call for help.

850
00:44:03,520 --> 00:44:05,520
His head bobbed up and down.

851
00:44:08,280 --> 00:44:10,520
The feeling from a year before...

852
00:44:10,760 --> 00:44:13,360
limbs trapped, sinking...

853
00:44:13,800 --> 00:44:15,199
choked me again.

854
00:44:16,399 --> 00:44:17,878
So when you ask

855
00:44:17,879 --> 00:44:20,560
if I'd help in a disaster,

856
00:44:23,280 --> 00:44:24,519
I'd say I don't know.

857
00:44:24,520 --> 00:44:25,560
Did he die?

858
00:44:26,040 --> 00:44:27,000
No.

859
00:44:27,040 --> 00:44:28,159
I rescued him again...

860
00:44:29,719 --> 00:44:31,279
I just hesitated a bit.

861
00:44:31,280 --> 00:44:33,679
But he'd been under too long asphyxiating,

862
00:44:34,239 --> 00:44:35,479
and ended up with brain damage.

863
00:44:35,520 --> 00:44:36,399
Later his parents

864
00:44:36,400 --> 00:44:38,040
knelt to thank me.

865
00:44:38,840 --> 00:44:40,520
After that I stopped swimming.

866
00:44:43,520 --> 00:44:45,639
You think his condition is your fault?

867
00:44:45,719 --> 00:44:47,119
Two minutes less,

868
00:44:47,120 --> 00:44:48,120
and he'd be fine?

869
00:44:49,159 --> 00:44:50,519
There are two other possibilities.

870
00:44:50,919 --> 00:44:53,679
He didn't end up with brain damaged but
dragged you under.

871
00:44:54,840 --> 00:44:55,919
Or you saved him

872
00:44:56,719 --> 00:44:58,159
and he turned on you again.

873
00:44:59,199 --> 00:45:00,199
Fan Xiao...

874
00:45:00,600 --> 00:45:02,760
could you comfort me like a normal person?

875
00:45:06,320 --> 00:45:07,439
You Shulang...

876
00:45:09,280 --> 00:45:10,600
you really are a good man.

877
00:45:11,080 --> 00:45:12,198
You said before

878
00:45:12,199 --> 00:45:14,199
we have no right to decide how others live
or die.

879
00:45:16,719 --> 00:45:17,719
But

880
00:45:17,840 --> 00:45:19,040
as long as we're alive,

881
00:45:20,320 --> 00:45:21,920
there will always be someone to tell you

882
00:45:23,239 --> 00:45:24,639
that the world isn't all bad...

883
00:45:25,399 --> 00:45:26,399
it can be beautiful.

884
00:45:28,600 --> 00:45:29,919
So you're that someone

885
00:45:31,000 --> 00:45:32,639
who tells me the world isn't all bad.

886
00:45:32,840 --> 00:45:34,159
I just want to tell you

887
00:45:35,399 --> 00:45:37,000
each of us

888
00:45:37,280 --> 00:45:39,199
has old wounds we can't face.

889
00:45:40,120 --> 00:45:41,320
Avoiding them isn't shameful,

890
00:45:41,399 --> 00:45:42,760
and it's not cowardly.

891
00:45:44,120 --> 00:45:46,280
We just need to let go.

892
00:45:46,320 --> 00:45:47,320
Let go.

893
00:45:52,600 --> 00:45:54,519
Don't obsess over whether you can face it.

894
00:45:54,520 --> 00:45:55,840
If you can't face the sea, don't.

895
00:45:56,760 --> 00:45:57,959
If you can't swim, don't.

896
00:46:03,159 --> 00:46:04,159
Fan Xiao...

897
00:46:04,360 --> 00:46:05,679
let's go back to the room.

898
00:46:05,719 --> 00:46:06,799
Lock the windows and doors,

899
00:46:07,280 --> 00:46:09,679
and we won't hear the damn waves.
